view

Class View

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.View
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.MouseListener, java.util.EventListener, javax.swing.event.TableModelListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CustomerView, FrontPageView, ReservationView, VehicleView

    public abstract class View
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.swing.event.TableModelListener, java.awt.event.MouseListener
    This class is the abstract superclass of all the views. It implements TableModelListener and MouseListener. The reason for this is that TableModelListener is used to add an action when the table is changed. The MouseListener is used to add an action to when the table is clicked on.
    Author:
    Michael Søby Andersen, msoa@itu.dk
